Body: Description: When Kaspersky Endpoint Security is active, NEP canÂ´t block access to personal Gmail accounts on MacOS Sequoia 15.2 (24C101).  When Kaspersky Endpoint Security is Off, NEP works Ok.  The same configurations are working on Windows (with Kaspersky EndPoint Security ON) and Linux Operating Systems.
What We've Learned Updated: When Kaspersky Endpoint Security is active the DPI is not working as expected.
Next Steps Updated: I asked the customer for some more details and I will set a meeting in order to collect a set of EPP Client logs.
